UPDATE!!
Sorry guys but that last version sucked abit.
Sure you could host a game with it, but no one could join.
I forgot to add a info_start point!*smacks forehead*
I made the level brighter though, added more p90s
and a little easter egg. : D

==============================
fy_cratedrop
by psychobadger
for Counter-Strike Source
==============================

A fun little map where you can drop crates
onto the opposing team while fighting.
Btw, you can use the crates to jump across to
the opposing side if they're arranged 
properly.

A fight yard map for 12 players.
Enjoy 
-psychobadger
